abstract: British Columbia Coroners Service announces opening of investigation after human foot, wearing running shoe, washes up on shore of Vancouver Island, 13th such finding since 2007.

headline.print_headline: The Americans; Canada: Another Foot Washes Ashore
headline.main: Canada: Another Human Foot Washes Ashore

snippet: The foot was found by a hiker on Vancouver Island’s Botanical Beach and was the 13th to wash up on British Columbia’s shoreline since 2007.
lead_paragraph: The foot was found by a hiker on Vancouver Island’s Botanical Beach and was the 13th to wash up on British Columbia’s shoreline since 2007.
